<section data-markdown>
<textarea data-template>

## Intermediate Vim

* `h/j/k/l` = move cursor left/down/up/right
* `c` = change (delete the next cursor movement, enter insert mode)
* `w` = word (move cursor forward by one word)
* `j` = move cursor down
* `b` = move back one word
* `.` = repeat last "edit"

</textarea>
</section>
