## Advanced Vim

```vim
:bufdo %s/\<subRoutine\>/newName/gc
```

* `bufdo` = repeat on all open files
* `%` = select the whole file
* `s` = substitute using regex
* `\<` = beginning of a word (regex)
* `\>` = end of a word (regex)
* `g` = all occurances on each line
* `c` = confirmation prompt
* `:help bufdo`
* `:help substitute`

</textarea>
